Supported API:
/v3/expand
Bitly::v3_expand('http://bit.ly/MiCtW6'); //return array, including 'http://google.com/'
http://dev.bitly.com/links.html#v3_expand

/v3/shorten
Bitly::v3_shorten('http://google.com/') //return array, including 'http://bit.ly/MiCtW6'
http://dev.bitly.com/links.html#v3_shorten


How to:
1.
Edit app/config/config.php
--
'packages'  => array(
    'bitly',
),
--

2.
Copy & Edit config/bitly.php
--
return array(
	'login' => 'YOUR_LOGIN',
	'apikey' => 'YOUR_APIKEY',
);
--

You can get login & apikey http://bitly.com/a/your_api_key
